Class Student

java.lang.Object
com.panotify.model.User
com.panotify.model.Student
public class Student extends User
Represents a student user in the PaNotify system. Extends the base User class with student-specific attributes and behaviors, such as enrolled courses and exam results.
Version:
1.0
Author:
PaNotify Team
